It is known that when using [some special characters|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CROWD/Characters+in+User+or+Group+DN%27s+that+will+cause+problems+when+using+Crowd] can cause the error stated in this [documentation|https://confluence.atlassian.com/x/kQnuEQ].

This produces the error:
{code}
Caused by: org.springframework.ldap.core.TokenMgrError: Lexical error at line x, column xx.  Encountered: "\\" (xx), after : ""
{code}

Confluence should allow the usage of special characters or workaround these.

